 rong></em><br />  Early Bird Registration: $60.00 (Before October 1\, 202
 6)<br />  Standard Registration: $80.00 (October 1 - November 15\, 2026)<
 /p><p>  &#160\;</p><p><strong>2026 Keynote Speakers:</strong></p><p>  Alu
